Like everyone should have a box of education and healthcare, so EWS or PwD quota is quite necessary.
But when it comes to quotas based on caste, I feel that equity prevails.

I see well-off people in OBCs, SC/STs who have proper facilities at their disposal taking quotas & relax.

"Life is inequitable !"

It is our learning dynamics which have brought us here.
